[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    253[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Care-plan reconciliation pipeline]                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    254[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Pulls from: EHR(s), referral-management system,     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    255[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      pharmacy system, home-health system, DME system,    │
